			SD [nSel] j * 0x10 + 0x40 + l
			SD [selX] l * 16 + 300
			SD [selY] j * 35 + 180
			SELBUILD nSel SI_DigitBig_7
				selX selY 1 0 8
				D 2 D 3
				0 0
				0 0
				0 0
				SEL_NONACTIVE
			SELBUILD nSel + 0x30 SI_DigitBig_8
				selX selY + 105 1 0 8
				D 2 D 3
				0 0
				0 0
				0 0
